France). After Sarralbe, investment abroad rapidly expanded, with additional locations in all parts of the world. Katoen Natie is now a global player. 1995 2000 Business Units In 2000, the activities were divided into customer-oriented business units. Katoen Natie works with this structure, to the great satisfaction of our customers. Katoen Natie today Today, Katoen Natie is a global supplier of value added logistics and applied engineering solutions. 2020 ... Back Katoen Natie Van Aerdtstraat 33 B-2060 Antwerpen info@katoennatie.com +32 3 221 68 11 LinkedIn Facebook Instagram YouTube Home Who we are Organisation Platforms Responsible Business History Philosophy Did you know People with passion Your industry Supply Chain Engineering Process Engineering Petrochemicals Specialty Chemicals Consumer Goods & Industry Port Operations General Cargo & Commodities Food & Feed Silo Cleaning Art Careers News Locations Contact Sitemap Downloads News 2022 © Katoen Natie. All rights reserved. - Cookie policy - Visitor’s privacy policy https://www.katoennatie.com/who-we-are/philosophy/ Philosophy - Katoen Natie General +32 3 221 68 11 Send us a message Find a location Home Who we are Organisation Platforms Responsible Business History Philosophy Did you know People with passion Your industry Supply Chain Engineering Process Engineering Petrochemicals Specialty Chemicals Consumer Goods & Industry Port Operations General Cargo & Commodities Food & Feed Silo Cleaning Art Careers News Locations Contact Back Philosophy Vision Requirements to logistics are becoming more and more intense. On one hand, customers become more demanding, on the other, distance between production and consumption locations becomes longer. This means that distribution becomes more global and more complex, whilst environmental and economical pressure is increasing. This means that our customers are constantly looking for more cost-efficient, reliable and sustainable solutions. Mission The mission of a company is